<p>10. &nbsp; &nbsp;Evaluation of carotid wall thickness and vertebro basilar system insufficiency in patients with obese polycystic ovary syndrome<br>Coksuer Hakan, Koplay Mustafa, Oghan Fatih, Haliloglu Berna, Keskin Nadi, Yayın Yeri: Journal of Obstetrics and Gynaecology Research, 2011<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>https://dx.doi.org/10.1111/j.1447-0756.2010.01472.x&nbsp;</p>
<p>11. &nbsp; &nbsp;Comparison of uterine artery blood flow with levonorgestrel intrauterine system and copper intrauterine device<br>Haliloglu Berna, Celik Aygen, Ilter Erdin, Bozkurt Serpil, Ozekici Umit, Yayın Yeri: Contraception, 2011<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp; https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.contraception.2010.09.001&nbsp;</p>
